   Date 22-05-2019
   Intitulé du poste recherché : Internship Opportunity July-August 2019
   Expérience professionnelle : Since October 2018 :
   Mechanical Engineer Apprentice
   RATP (Parisian Public Transports)
   Tests and Measurements Laboratory
   Mechanical Division
   Projects:
   ? Development of an interactive map of all acoustics reports
   between 2011 and 2018 (more than 600). In order to do this, I
   read acoustic reports and acoustic standards. Then I summarised the
   data and used Google Fusion Tables in order to filter and display the
   data on a map.
   ? Help to the acoustic team to carry out the acoustic measurements.
   ? Development of a noise indicator for employees in maintenance
   workshops. I managed (I wrote functional specifications and
   planned the deadlines) and do the project (I wrote a computer
   program, chose the components and designed the box)
   July and August 2018 :
   Cleaning operative
