   Mans) - Engineering School of Le Mans - Apprenticeship :
   Specialising in Vibrations, Acoustics, Sensors
   Expected graduation date: September 2021
   Courses: mechanics, acoustics, electronics, computer programming
   mathematics, optics, physics of materials
   Projects: design and study of a music instrument, design of an
   electronic game (Arduino)
   2016-2018 Two years of preparation for admission to French Engineering
   Schools :
   École Nationale Supérieure d’Ingénieurs du Mans - Le Mans 72000
   Lycée Clemenceau - Nantes 44000
   Mathematics, Physics, Engineering Sciences
   June 2016 Baccalauréat, French equivalent to the Higher Leaving
   Certificate
   with highest honours
