   Mans, France. I am doing this by working 50% of my time at school and
   50% in a work placement at RATP in the Tests and Measurements
   Laboratory. I am looking for an internship abroad in July and August
   2019. The purpose of this internship is to discover the professional
   world abroad and to learn foreign work methods by supporting an
   engineer or a technician.
